Native Plants Analysis

library(vegan)
library(broom)
library(tidyverse)
long_pcoa <- function(x){
  require(vegan)
  x2 <- x %>% 
    dplyr::select(SampleID, variable, RA, Compartment, host_common_name) %>% 
    spread(variable, RA, fill = 0)
  pc <- capscale(log2(x2[,4:ncol(x2)] + 1) ~ 1)
  pc.axes <- bind_cols(x2[,1:3], as_tibble(scores(pc, choices = c(1:5))$sites))
  pc.eig <- eigenvals(pc) / sum(eigenvals(pc))
  pc.results <- list(axes = pc.axes, eig = pc.eig)
  return(pc.results)
}
long_pcoa <- function(x, samples = "SampleID", otus = "variable", value = "RA", dist = "bray"){
  metadata <- x %>% dplyr::ungroup() %>% 
    dplyr::select_(-otus, -value) %>% 
    dplyr::group_by_(samples) %>% 
    dplyr::distinct()
  return(metadata)
}
joe <- long_pcoa(nExp)
